''' Sî Bengal ''' ([[Bengal-ngî]]: পশ্চিম বঙ্গ; {{lang-ne|पश्चिम बङ्गाल}}; {{lang-en|'''West Bengal'''}}), [[Yin-thu]] yit-ke vi-yî tûng-phu ke [[pâng]], chhai [[Bangladesh thi-khî]] sî-phu, tûng-phu phî lièn [[Bangladesh]] fò [[Assam]], sî-phu fò [[Orissa]], [[Bihar]] yî-khi̍p [[Jharkhand]] siông-lièn, pet phóng [[Bhutan]] fò [[Sikkim]], nàm-phîn [[Bengal vân]]. Mien-chit 88,752 phìn-fông kûng-lî, ngìn-khiéu yok 8 chhiên van, chú-yeu he [[Bengal ngìn]], pâng kôn-fông ngî-ngièn he [[Bengal-ngî]]. Sú-fú vi-yî [[Kolkata]], vì Yin-thu thi-sâm-thai sàng-sṳ.
